Requisisão HTTP

URL: https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/ ?type=grass&name=1
        ${IP}/${path = caminho de identificação do recurso}

Request Method: GET | POST | PUT | DELETE | PATCH

Query string
type = grass
name = 1

